Class Crew

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Crew

  • public class Crew
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds and stores an ArrayList of Person types. Stores their ship, food, medical items and cash.

    cam, grey

        public Person createCrewMember(java.lang.String name,
                               int i,
                               java.lang.String race)
        Switch statement to create a Person object of specific race. Uses int's from 1-6 as cases. Defaults to Human to make invalid user input easier to deal with for command-line mode.
        Parameters:
        name - String that holds crew member's name
        i - Unique identifying int
        race - String race to select
        Returns:
        Person object
